<div id="pf3b89" class="pf w5d h233" data-page-no="3b89"><div class="pc pc3b89 w5d h233"><div class="t m3ef4 x66 h234 y2108 ff3 fs72 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">CHARISMIsk </div><div class="t m3723 x4e h234 y14bf ff3 fs72 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">OF 1HE SPIRIT </div><div class="t mebb x4a h1df y1167 ff1 fs35 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">by Rene </div><div class="t m104a x36 h28 y10be ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Currently, speaking in tongues is the rage of over 50 Christian </div><div class="t m6ec x14 h28 y1368 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">denominations throughout America. And the movement is growing. </div><div class="t m3c1 x14 h28 y1369 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Catholics, Methodists, Episcopalians, Baptists, and others thrill with </div><div class="t m55c x14 h28 y10cd ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">what they believe to be the true language of the Holy Spirit. </div><div class="t mcdb x36 h28 y136a ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What does it mean to open the door to semiunconsciousness so that </div><div class="t mdd9 x14 h28 y1234 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">an unknown tongue can emerge? What is it that rushes in to cause the </div><div class="t m74c x14 h28 y1d72 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tumbling, melodic sounds? </div><div class="t mae4 x36 h28 y136b ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Speaking in tongues. One man stands aside. Listens intently to the </div><div class="t m23e x14 h28 y7d4 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sounds of ecstasy, watches the events taking place, speaks to key </div><div class="t m559 x14 h28 y1c2f ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">people. Refers to history for comparison. He writes a book. </div><div class="t m9fc x28 h28 y136c ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Rene Noorbergen&apos;s CHARISMA OF THE SPIRIT investigates the </div><div class="t m177 x14 h28 y12a3 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tongues movement. Hear it from various ministers of the churches </div><div class="t md0c x14 h28 y747 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">involved, from participating church member&apos;s, from language experts, </div><div class="t mf25 x14 h28 y1cc8 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and, for contrast, from representatives of the psychic world. </div><div class="t m146f x28 h28 y1c2a ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Because the tongues movement is becoming more powerful as time </div><div class="t m573 x14 h28 yd3f ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">goes on, we ask, &quot;What does it </div><div class="t ma23 x14 h28 y136f ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">mean?&quot; You will find that CHA-</div><div class="t m390 x14 h28 y108d ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">RISMA OF THE SPIRIT, is an aid </div><div class="t m648 x14 h28 y1107 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to understanding the supernatural </div><div class="t meb8 x14 h28 yb83 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">experience of tongues. </div><div class="t m7cd x28 h28 ye66 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Get your copy of CHARISMA </div><div class="t m452 x14 h28 y1442 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">OF THE SPIRIT from your Ad-</div><div class="t ma29 x14 h28 y1190 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ventist Book Center. Or from ABC </div><div class="t ma58 x14 h28 y1223 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Mailing Service, 2621 Farnam </div><div class="t m755 x14 h28 y108f ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Street, Omaha, NB 68131. In Can-</div><div class="t ma63 x14 h28 y11e8 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ada: 201 16th Avenue NE, Calgary, </div><div class="t m13e x5d h28 y1032 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Alberta T2E 1J9. Include 30 cents </div><div class="t m104c x14 h28 y1cc0 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">shipping and handling for first </div><div class="t mb52 x14 h28 y1443 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">copy, 10 cents each additional. Tax </div><div class="t mdf7 x5d h28 y1151 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">if applicable. </div><div class="t m3db x5d h28 y14fd ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Brought to you by </div><div class="t mb35 x5d h28 y14fe ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Pacific Press. </div><div class="t m5 x41 h28 y14fd ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">î˜‰</div><div class="t m4742 x68 h28 y1444 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">125 </div><div class="t m2245 x14 h6f y1d6b